high_descs: Turn right and go to the edge of the bed.
Pick up the round brown pillow on the bed.
Go to the desklamp behind you.
anns.task_desc: Turn on a DeskLamp while holding a long round brown cylinder.

high_descs: Walk over to the side of the bed near the end of the bed.
Pick up the pink pillow that is on the bed next to the box.
Walk over to the side of the desklamp.
Turn on the desklamp on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Look at a Pillow in the DeskLamp light.

high_descs: Turn around and move towards the bed in the bedroom.
Take the pillow from the bed
Turn around and move towards the desklamp.
Turn on the desklamp on the table.
anns.task_desc: Turn on the Pillow on the DeskLamp
